ge-349371\" style=\"max-width: 355px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-349371\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Switch editor themes using the setting in the right column at Appearance > Custom CSS.</p></div>\n<p>If you have any queries or requests, please, let us know. Free support is available on the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/thread/\">SiteOrigin forum</a>. Quick email support with a wide scope is available <a href=\"mailto:support@siteorigin.com\">via email</a> for all SiteOrigin Premium users.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/dark-theme-now-available-in-siteorigin-css/\">Dark Theme Now Available in SiteOrigin CSS</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://siteorigin.com/dark-theme-now-available-in-siteorigin-css/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"WPML Translation Editor  Page Builder Compatibility\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/\";s:7:\"at